thread.title: Rich
thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Rich

author: Rich
title: Rich
text:
I've tried the other boxes out there and let me say that what you get in the box matters and Lucky puts way better baits in the box than Mystery. There's no comparison. I've never received discontinued or overstock bait from Lucky but I have received that garbage from Mystery Tackle Box.
If I'm spending my hard earned money, then I'm picking Lucky Tackle Box.
